Phidias - A Tracker based feed reader
===============================================================================

Phidias is a viewer for feeds stored in Tracker, which items visualization is
plugginable and customizzable.

Tracker homepage is available at: http://www.gnome.org/projects/tracker/
Phidias homepage is available at: http://phidias.barberaware.org/

REQUIREMENTS
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Phidias depends on:

  - tracker-client-0.8 >= 0.8.1
  - dbus-glib-1 >= 0.82
  - webkit-1.0 >= 1.1.15.4
  - champlain-gtk-0.4 >= 0.4.2
  - clutter-gtk-0.10 >= 0.10.2
  - libgrss >= 0.4

INSTALLATION
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
See INSTALL file.

